.DT
set_strict_currency
Disk World creator help
set_strict_currency

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_strict_currency -  This method controls whether or not a shop will accept currency from the "default" area.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_strict_currency(int new_strict)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^new_strict%^RESET%^ - set this to 1 if the shop should only accept currency
from the current area it is in (determined by the "place" property).

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/shops/general_shop.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method controls whether or not a shop will accept currency
from the "default" area.
.EP

